item.title: CVE-2023-5943|2024-01-29T14:44:25.295Z -- unknown -- wp-adv-quiz
item.description: The Wp-Adv-Quiz WordPress plugin before 1.0.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when unfiltered_html is disallowed.

item.title: CVE-2023-5956|2024-01-29T14:44:20.684Z -- unknown -- wp-adv-quiz
item.description: The Wp-Adv-Quiz WordPress plugin through 1.0.2 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup).
